+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RH1m1UoixismxLuQpt16ew","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Starting autopilot. I'll narrate each decision and move quickly since the requirements are well-defined.\n\n**Q: Overall architecture pattern?**\n→ Choosing: Layered architecture (routes → middleware → storage)\n  Reasoning: Express app with route modules, auth middleware, and in-memory stores. Simple, fits the scope, no over-engineering.\n\n**Q: Data storage approach?**\n→ Choosing: Maps keyed by UUID for each entity type\n  Reasoning: O(1) lookups by ID, simple iteration for queries. Maps for users, folders, documents, shares, activity log as array.\n\n**Q: Authentication approach?**\n→ Choosing: Simple random token stored in a Map (token → userId)\n  Reasoning: No need for JWT complexity for in-memory only system. Random hex tokens are sufficient.\n\n**Q: Route structure?**\n→ Choosing: Resource-based REST routes\n  - `POST /auth/register`, `POST /auth/login`\n  - CRUD on `/folders/:id`, `/documents/:id`\n  - `POST /documents/:id/share`, `POST /folders/:id/share`\n  - `GET /activity`\n  Reasoning: Clean, intuitive, standard REST patterns.\n\n**Q: Permission inheritance model?**\n→ Choosing: Folder permissions cascade to documents within. Most permissive role wins when multiple paths exist.\n  Reasoning: Matches requirements. Check direct share + folder share, pick highest role.\n\n**Q: File organization?**\n→ Choosing: Single `src/app.ts` with modular sections\n  Reasoning: For a project of this size, a single well-organized file is simpler than splitting into many tiny files. Export `createApp()`.\n\nNow let me write the design document and proceed to implementation."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":272,"cache_read_input_tokens":23680,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":272},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"139119ac-2358-47de-bf5f-afc4a602d926","uuid":"a7e33eb7-4690-4792-bb83-edd1461fd3ce"}
